# Generated docs site (build artifacts of `make site` / tools/gensite).
# docs/*.md is the source of truth; the themed HTML is published to gh-pages
# separately and never committed on this branch. These patterns match ONLY the
# generated index.html under docs/ — NOT the hand-authored landing /index.html
# at the repo root, nor any .md source.
/docs/index.html
/docs/*/index.html
/docs/*/*/index.html